@startuml locker-state-loker-pintar-fst
title State Machine — Siklus Hidup Loker (scripts/data.js)

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #F4F1E8
  BorderColor #2A403C
  ArrowColor #2A403C
}

state "AVAILABLE\n(kosong, bisa dialokasikan)" as Available
state "DELIVERING\n(direservasi kurir,\ntitipan berlangsung)" as Delivering
state "OCCUPIED\n(terisi; ownerNip terisi)" as Occupied

[*] --> Available : seed()\n(loker tanpa pemilik tetap)
[*] --> Occupied : seed()\n(loker permanen staf)

Available --> Delivering : reserveLocker(id)\nlayar Courier — Assign dimuat

Delivering --> Available : releaseLocker(id)\nBatal / "Ganti Ukuran" /\nidle timeout 60s
Delivering --> Occupied : occupyLocker(id, nip)\n+ recordDelivery()\n"Sudah Diletakkan"

Occupied --> Available : claimMail(id)\nloker non-permanen &\ntidak ada mail tersisa
Occupied --> Occupied : claimMail(id)\nloker permanen staf\n(tetap milik pemilik)

note bottom of Delivering
  Semua transisi dijaga di DataRepository:
  fungsi menolak (return null) jika
  from-state tidak sesuai, sehingga
  pemanggilan liar tidak merusak inventori.
end note

@enduml
